OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend 37 times showed
OL,4,C'clear thinking', court hears
OL,6,FA man who killed his best friend on
OL,7,FChristmas Eve was demonstrating "clear
OL,8,Fthinking" in the hours before the
OL,9,Fattack, a jury has heard during a
OL,10,Ftrial at Cardiff Crown Court.
OL,12,FDylan Thomas, now 24, stabbed William
OL,13,FBush 37 times in the Llandaff area of
OL,14,FCardiff on December 24th 2023.
OL,16,FMr Thomas has previously pleaded
OL,17,Fguilty to manslaughter on the grounds
OL,18,Fof diminished responsibility, but
OL,19,Fdenies murder.
