OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend 37 times showed
OL,4,C'clear thinking', court hears
OL,6,FA jury has already heard evidence from
OL,7,Fa forensic psychiatrist who told the
OL,8,Fcourt he believed Thomas had been
OL,9,Fpsychotic "for many months" before the
OL,10,Ffatal incident.
OL,12,FMr Bush sustained serious wounds to
OL,13,Fhis neck during what the prosecution
OL,14,Fdescribed as a "frenzied attack" and
OL,15,Fdied at the scene.
OL,17,FOn Wednesday, while concluding the
OL,18,Fprosecution's case, Mr Greg Bull KC
OL,19,Ftold the court that the defendant and
OL,20,Fthe victim "were good friends".
