OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend 37 times showed
OL,4,C'clear thinking', court hears
OL,6,F"Whereas on the other side of the
OL,7,Fcoin, Mr Bush, having come from very
OL,8,Flittle, achieved great success in his
OL,9,Fpersonal life... Everything in his
OL,10,Flife was on the up where it might have
OL,11,Fbeen perceived in Dylan Thomas' case,
OL,12,Flife was on the downward spiral."
OL,14,FThomas told police he had acted in
OL,15,Fself defence, but Mr Bull said Thomas
OL,16,Fhad shown "clear thinking."
OL,18,F"These sort of wounds, we say, show
OL,19,Fhis attacker showed an intention to
OL,20,Fkill", Mr Bull said.
