OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend 37 times showed
OL,4,C'clear thinking', court hears
OL,6,FIn concluding the defence case, Mr
OL,7,FOrlando Pownall KC said that the only
OL,8,Fexplanation for Mr Thomas' actions was
OL,9,Fthat his psychotic state had
OL,10,Fsubstantially impaired his ability to
OL,11,Fform a rational judgement or self
OL,12,Fcontrol.
OL,14,FReferring to the prosecution's case,
OL,15,FMr Pownall said: "(the suggestion)
OL,16,Fthat a sudden considered loss of
OL,17,Ftemper could have nothing to do with
OL,18,Fhis mental state, is untenable."
