OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend 37 times showed
OL,4,C'clear thinking', court hears
OL,6,FEarlier in the trial Dr Panchu Xavier,
OL,7,Fa consultant forensic psychiatrist at
OL,8,FAshworth High Secure Hospital, where
OL,9,Fthe defendant is being treated for
OL,10,Fschizophrenia, told the court: "My
OL,11,Fview is that he was convinced he was
OL,12,Fgoing to come to harm", Dr Xavier said.
OL,14,F"If that is what you think, you are
OL,15,Fgoing to try to eliminate that threat."
OL,17,F"In his mind, that's why he behaved as
OL,18,Fhe did. He felt threatened by his best
OL,19,Ffriend and that's why he responded as
OL,20,Fhe did.
