OL,6,F"The jury has previously heard that Mr
OL,7,FThomas initially stabbed Mr Bush in
OL,8,Fhis bedroom, before chasing him down
OL,9,Fthe stairs of the 3 storey house they
OL,10,Fshared in Cardiff where the assault
OL,11,Fcontinued.
OL,13,FDefence barrister Mr Pownall painted a
OL,14,Fpicture to the court of the confused
OL,15,Fand troubled mind of Dylan Thomas in
OL,16,Fthe hours before the attack.
