OL,3,CMan who stabbed friend 37 times showed
OL,4,C'clear thinking', court hears
OL,6,FHe referred the jury to the seemingly
OL,7,Frandom and varied searches he made on
OL,8,Fthe night of 23rd December, including
OL,9,Fmethods of overdosing and assisted
OL,10,Fsuicide, and said that these were
OL,11,Fevidence themselves of his psychotic
OL,12,Fmental state.
OL,14,FThomas has been appearing in court via
OL,15,Fvideo link from a maximum security
OL,16,Fhospital in Liverpool, where he has
OL,17,Fbeen living for 8 months.
OL,19,FThe trial, being heard in front of
OL,20,FJudge Lady Justice Karen Steyn,
OL,21,Fcontinues.
